Equivalent to [`CString::as_bytes()`] except that the
returned slice includes the trailing nul terminator.

# Examples

```
use std::ffi::CString;

let c_string = CString::from(c"foo");
let bytes = c_string.as_bytes_with_nul();
assert_eq!(bytes, &[b'f', b'o', b'o', b'\0']);
```
